::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod fires a few shots at the retreating Predicons.
"Maximal's, we have driven off the Predicons. We have won.
Victory is our's!" Hot Rod activates his comlink.
"All Maximals, this is Hot Rod. The Cybertronian Fire is secure. The
Preds are gone. We won." Hot Rod sits on a rock.
"Well we srvived the scouts. Now we wait for the rest of them." He says.
